Citation.sAbstract: The solubilities of lovastatin in binary acetone + water solvent mixtures were determined by the synthetic  method from (277.35 to 310.05) K by a laser monitoring observation technique. Results of these measurements  were correlated by the semiempirical equation. For the nine mole fractions of acetone studied, a semiempirical  equation was found to provide an accurate mathematical representation of the experimental data.
Citation.sTitle: Solubility of Lovastatin in Acetone + Water Solvent Mixtures
